name: hidden riddles
description:
Some stash it in their archives, some try to throw it away, some are just hidden in a plain sight. In the end, the truth will slip eventually and revealed itself. 

Do you hide your riddles well? 🤫

–

Second NFT collab project of Jefta Mikola, Yosephine Salim and Karin Josephine. Karin is responsible for visualizing the mosaic fragments, while Jefta is here to enliven it with a few beats. Epin frames the thread between visuals and the beats through her narratives.
